<td headers="stub_1_10 title" class="gt_row gt_left gt_striped" style="font-weight: bold;">Optimal Designs for state estimation in electricity networks</td>
<td headers="stub_1_10 abstract" class="gt_row gt_left gt_striped"></td></tr>
